{"type":"champion","format":"standAloneComplex","version":"4.16.1","data":{"Azir":{"id":"Azir","key":"268","name":"沙漠皇帝","title":"阿兹尔","image":{"full":"Azir.png","sprite":"champion4.png","group":"champion","x":0,"y":0,"w":48,"h":48},"skins":[{"id":"268000","num":0,"name":"default"},{"id":"268001","num":1,"name":"星际之门 阿兹尔"}],"lore":"Once a mortal man blinded by his own hubris, Azir has recently returned as an Ascended being with unmatched dominion over the burning sands. He seeks to restore Shurima to its former glory, but some dispute his right to rule them. Azir’s power, however, is undeniable.","blurb":"Once a mortal man blinded by his own hubris, Azir has recently returned as an Ascended being with unmatched dominion over the burning sands. He seeks to restore Shurima to its former glory, but some dispute his right to rule them. Azir’s power, ...","allytips":["Be careful about putting down both of the soldiers stored by Arise! Unless you're going all-in, always have a soldier in your back pocket if you need to escape over a wall or if you misposition your other soldier and need damage now.","In the lane, try to position your soldiers between the enemy's minions and the enemy champion. This way you can use them both to last hit and to project threat onto your lane opponent.","Think of Emperor's Divide as a defensive ability first and foremost. Use it when the enemy engages on you or your allies. Remember that your team can walk through the soldiers summoned by Emperor's Divide and use this to your advantage when enemy melee champions engage on you.","Be a bird!"],"enemytips":["阿兹尔依靠他的士兵来输出伤害，并且每移动一次士兵就要等待一段时间。尽量在他的士兵无法移动时来赚取优势。","阿兹尔的持续输出非常可观，但缺乏其他法师那样的一次性爆发伤害。尽量在他能发起反击之前把他轰杀掉。","请试着把黄沙士兵看成火焰。不要站在火焰之中。"],"tags":["Mage","Marksman"],"partype":"Mana","info":{"attack":6,"defense":3,"magic":8,"difficulty":9},"stats":{"hp":390.0,"hpperlevel":80.0,"mp":280.0,"mpperlevel":42.0,"movespeed":335.0,"armor":14.0,"armorperlevel":3.0,"spellblock":30.0,"spellblockperlevel":0.0,"attackrange":525.0,"hpregen":6.0,"hpregenperlevel":0.55,"mpregen":6.5,"mpregenperlevel":0.65,"crit":0.0,"critperlevel":0.0,"attackdamage":43.0,"attackdamageperlevel":2.8,"attackspeedoffset":0.1,"attackspeedperlevel":1.5},"spells":[{"id":"AzirQ","name":"狂沙猛攻","description":"阿兹尔命令所有黄沙士兵朝着目标地点发起冲锋。黄沙士兵会对沿途的所有目标造成魔法伤害，并施加持续1秒的可叠加减速效果。","tooltip":"阿兹尔命令所有<span class=\"colorEED6AF\">黄沙士兵</span>朝目标地点发起冲锋。<span class=\"colorEED6AF\">黄沙士兵</span>会对沿途的所有敌人造成{{ e1 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">(+{{ a1 }})</span>魔法伤害和一层@Effect2Amount*-100@%减速效果。这个减速效果持续1秒，并且可以叠加。","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[10,9,8,7,6],"cooldownBurn":"10/9/8/7/6","cost":[70,70,70,70,70],"costBurn":"70","effect":[null,[60,90,120,150,180]],"effectBurn":[null,"60/90/120/150/180"],"vars":[{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.5,"key":"a1"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[800,800,800,800,800],"rangeBurn":"800","image":{"full":"AzirQ.png","sprite":"spell13.png","group":"spell","x":384,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }}法力"},{"id":"AzirW","name":"沙兵现身","description":"阿兹尔召唤一个黄沙士兵来为他攻击附近的敌方单位。如果敌方单位在士兵的攻击距离内，那么士兵会代替阿兹尔进行普攻。士兵的攻击会对一条直线上的敌人造成魔法伤害。","tooltip":"阿兹尔召唤出一个持续{{ e1 }}秒的<span class=\"colorEED6AF\">黄沙士兵</span>。在阿兹尔对一名敌人进行普攻时，如果该名敌人在某个黄沙士兵的攻击范围内，那么这名黄沙士兵会代替阿兹尔进行攻击，对一条直线上的造成{{ f2 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">(+{{ a1 }})</span>魔法伤害。如果有多个士兵对相同目标进行攻击，那么除第一个士兵外的其它士兵只造成25%伤害。即使敌人不在阿兹尔的攻击范围内，阿兹尔也能操纵黄沙士兵对这个敌人进行攻击。<br><br>阿兹尔最多可储存{{ maxammo }}个<span class=\"colorEED6AF\">黄沙士兵</span>。每过<span class=\"colorFFFFFF\">{{ f1 }}</span>秒，就有一个黄沙士兵整装待发。离黄沙士兵太远的话，他们就会被遣散。<span class=\"colorEED6AF\">黄沙士兵</span>在敌方防御塔附近时，消散速度会翻倍。<br><br>阿兹尔可以在敌方防御塔上召唤士兵，从而消耗士兵来对防御塔直接造成伤害。这样做会对防御塔造成{{ f4 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">(+{{ a2 }})</span>魔法伤害。","leveltip":{"label":["再装填时间"],"effect":["{{ f1 }} -> {{ f3 }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[1.5,1.5,1.5,1.5,1.5],"cooldownBurn":"1.5","cost":[40,40,40,40,40],"costBurn":"40","effect":[null,[9,9,9,9,9],[12,11,10,9,8]],"effectBurn":[null,"9","12/11/10/9/8"],"vars":[{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.7,"key":"a1"},{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.7,"key":"a2"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[450,450,450,450,450],"rangeBurn":"450","image":{"full":"AzirW.png","sprite":"spell13.png","group":"spell","x":432,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }}法力"},{"id":"AzirE","name":"流沙移形","description":"阿兹尔冲向他的一个黄沙士兵，击飞并伤害敌人。如果他命中了一位敌方英雄，那么他就会获得护盾。","tooltip":"阿兹尔突进到他的一个<span class=\"colorEED6AF\">黄沙士兵</span>身旁，对命中的敌人造成{{ e3 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">(+{{ a1 }})</span>魔法伤害和{{ e1 }}秒击飞效果。如果阿兹尔命中了一名敌方英雄，那么他会停下来并获得持续{{ e6 }}秒的护盾，护盾可以吸收{{ e4 }}<span class=\"colorFF3300\">(+{{ f1 }})[15%额外生命值]</span>伤害。","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","冷却时间","护盾"],"effect":["{{ e3 }} -> {{ e3NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}","{{ e4 }} -> {{ e4NL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[19,18,17,16,15],"cooldownBurn":"19/18/17/16/15","cost":[60,60,60,60,60],"costBurn":"60","effect":[null,[0.5,0.5,0.5,0.5,0.5],[19,18,17,16,15],[60,90,120,150,180],[60,100,140,180,220],null,[4,4,4,4,4]],"effectBurn":[null,"0.5","19/18/17/16/15","60/90/120/150/180","60/100/140/180/220",null,"4"],"vars":[{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.4,"key":"a1"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[1100,1100,1100,1100,1100],"rangeBurn":"1100","image":{"full":"AzirE.png","sprite":"spell14.png","group":"spell","x":0,"y":0,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }}法力"},{"id":"AzirR","name":"禁军之墙","description":"阿兹尔召唤一道由禁军组成的人墙向前冲锋，对敌人造成伤害和击退效果。","tooltip":"阿兹尔召唤一道由禁军组成的人墙向前冲锋，击退沿途的敌人并造成{{ e1 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">(+{{ a1 }})</span>魔法伤害。然后这道由禁军组成的人墙会持续{{ e4 }}秒。<br><br>敌方英雄将会被禁军之墙所阻挡，并且无法用突进技能穿过这道人墙，而<span class=\"colorFFF673\">阿兹尔和他的友军可以自由穿过</span>并在穿过人墙时获得{{ e5 }}%移动速度加成。<br><br>禁军之墙不会与阿兹尔的攻击或技能进行互动。","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","士兵数量","持续时长","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ e3 }} -> {{ e3NL }}","{{ e4 }} -> {{ e4NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":3,"cooldown":[140,120,100],"cooldownBurn":"140/120/100","cost":[100